ASQUITH, Herbert Henry, 1st Earl of Oxford and Asquith (1852-1928)

Plaque erected in 1951 by London County Council at 20 Cavendish Square, Marylebone, London, W1G 0RN, City of Westminster

Profession

Politician

Category

Politics and Administration

Inscription

HERBERT HENRY ASQUITH 1st EARL OF OXFORD AND ASQUITH 1852-1928 STATESMAN lived here
